<title>AUSTRALIA: Datacraft returns to profit in 1996/97.</title>
<headline>Datacraft returns to profit in 1996/97.</headline>
<dateline>MELBOURNE 1997-08-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Year to June 30</p>
<p>		 (million A$ unless stated)</p>
<p>    Operating profit		    14.75 vs 0.60</p>
<p>    Net			     profit 6.91 vs loss 8.89</p>
<p>    Sales				  270.62 vs 193.06</p>
<p>    Other income			   7.20 vs 3.62</p>
<p>    Shr (cents)		     gain 6.54 vs loss 8.72</p>
<p>    Abnormal items		profit 0.96 vs loss 6.49</p>
<p>    Tax			    expense 2.94 vs credit 0.68</p>
<p>    Interest				 3.64 vs 1.54</p>
<p>    Depreciation			   6.94 vs 6.39</p>
<p>    Minorities			     5.85 vs 3.67</p>
<p>NOTE: Datacraft Ltd is a data communications equipment manufacturer, importer and designer. It also controls Singapore-based Datacraft Asia Ltd</p>
<p>-- Sydney Newsroom 61-2 9373-1800</p>
